dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Eagle Rest Peak/ South 1/4 of Conner SW quadrangles, Kern County, California
dct_alternative_sm: Eagle Rest Peak and Conner SW map
Geology Eagle Rest Peak and Conner SW quadrangles
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle EAGLE REST PEAK, CA 1991, NIMA 2153 I NW -- Series V895; CONNER SW, CA 1995 AMS 2154 II SW -- Series V895; photorevised 1968 and 1973."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
